# Rocket.new — Notepads (Persistent Reusable Context)

> Notepads are different from Rules.
> Rules = always-on constraints (what NOT to do)
> Notepads = on-demand templates you inject when needed (HOW to do specific things)

---

## What Notepads Are

Notepads store reusable prompts, code templates, and context blocks.
You reference them with `@notepad-name` in any Cursor chat.
They inject the full template content into your prompt instantly.

**Access**: Cursor → View → Notepads (or Cmd+Shift+N)

---

## Pre-Built Notepads (Ready to Use)

Five notepads are already created in `.cursor/notepads/`:

| Notepad File | Reference With | Contents |
