### Notepad 4: `new-feature-checklist`
```
Content to store:

When implementing any new feature in a Rocket.new project, verify:

SCHEMA:
□ New table has: id (uuid), user_id (uuid FK → auth.users ON DELETE CASCADE), created_at
□ Index on user_id: CREATE INDEX table_user_id_idx ON table(user_id)
□ RLS enabled with all 4 CRUD policies
□ Migration SQL saved to supabase/migrations/

API:
□ Route at app/api/[name]/route.ts
□ getUser() check before any data access
□ Typed Supabase response with generics
□ Proper error codes (401, 400, 500)

UI:
□ Server Component for data fetching
□ Client Component only where hooks/events needed
□ loading.tsx alongside page.tsx
□ Empty state handled

AUTH:
□ Route inside (protected)/ group OR explicit getUser() + redirect
□ RLS provides database-level backup protection

VERIFY:
□ npx tsc --noEmit clean
□ Test as two different users — second user cannot see first user's data
```

**Usage**: `@new-feature-checklist I just implemented user notifications — verify everything is correct`

