## How to Create a Notepad

1. Cursor → View → Notepads
2. Click "New Notepad"
3. Name it (this becomes `@notepad-name`)
4. Paste the template content
5. Save

## How to Use a Notepad

In any Cursor chat:
```
@rls-template for the subscriptions table
@api-route-template for a DELETE endpoint that removes a project
@new-feature-checklist I just finished the file upload feature
```

The notepad content is injected directly into your prompt as context.
